---

### 🔸 Window Function (Ranking)

```python id="bx2m1p"
row_number().over(Window.partitionBy("city").orderBy(desc("total_spent")))
```

---

## ⚠️ Challenges Faced

### 🔹 Data Quality Issues

Handling missing and invalid values without losing important data.

---

### 🔹 Schema Mismatch

Ensuring correct data types for calculations and joins.

---

### 🔹 Join Accuracy

Ensuring proper joins using `customer_id` to avoid incorrect results.

---

### 🔹 Implementing Business Logic

Designing meaningful transformations like repeat customers and top spenders.

---

